data.description: You'll love coming home to this impressive, four bedroom Colonial located in the sought after College Green subdivision!  Huge kitchen features stainless steel appliances including a new refrigerator, Corian countertops and soft close cabinets.  Tons of closet space throughout the home.  Partially finished basement.  New Sump Pump (2023) Newer Furnace (2022) Newer hot water tank.  New Gas Fireplace with electrical insert.  New electrical box (2017) New WIFI garage door opener system.  Large, partially fenced in backyard features paved stone patio and gas hookup.  Extra driveway space next to the garage.
